		<div class="post-956 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-heresy category-politics category-publicity-bitch category-ramayana category-religion category-sita-sings-the-blues category-the-interwebs category-where-is-everyone" id="post-956">


<div class="post-headline">		<h1>Ban &#8220;Sita Sings the Blues&#8221; from the Internet!</h1>
		</div>

<div class="post-bodycopy clearfix"><p>Seriously, I could use the publicity. What would happen if thousands of people <a href="http://www.ipetitions.com/petition/sitasingstheblues/" target="_blank">signed this petition</a>? Has a movie ever been banned from the Internet before? I want to see how it&#8217;s done. You can leave a message with your signature. They only have 367 so far &#8211; do your part, people.</p>
<div class="plus-one-wrap"><g:plusone href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/01/08/ban-sita-sings-the-blues-from-the-internet/"></g:plusone></div><div class="addtoany_share_save_container"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="wpa2a_3"><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save" style="background:url(http://blog.ninapaley.com/wp-content/plugins/add-to-any/favicon.png) no-repeat scroll 4px 0px !important;padding:0 0 0 25px;display:inline-block;height:16px;vertical-align:middle">Share/Bookmark</a></div></div><p class="wp-flattr-button"><a class="FlattrButton" style="display:none;" href="http://blog.ninapaley.com/2010/01/08/ban-sita-sings-the-blues-from-the-internet/" title=" Ban &#8220;Sita Sings the Blues&#8221; from the Internet!" rev="flattr;uid:ninapaley;language:en_GB;category:text;tags:blog;button:compact;">Seriously, I could use the publicity. What would happen if thousands of people signed this petition? Has a movie ever been banned from the Internet before? I want to see...</a></p></div>

